{"tid":1809438,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"迫使藍絲支持黃金經濟圈","createTime":"2020-01-03T05:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T08:16:11.000Z","uid":44646,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9cafe88113a80977dabcc80a95ed4e1ae079a0dd","tid":1809438,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:59:37.000Z","msg":"迫使藍絲支持黃金經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n黃金經濟圈越做越大，但總有少數派藍絲基於立場唔幫襯黃店<br />\n如何迫使藍絲都在黃金圈消費？<br />\n我有一計<br />\n<br />\n簡單講，趁過年以黃金經濟圈購物券取代現金作為利是<br />\n大家想像一下，好多中產和理非每年都派皮幾兩皮利是<br />\n反正已出之物，何不大手購入黃營禮券作利是<br />\n收利是小朋友自已唔識用大可同父母兌換<br />\n結果係黃店有先期收入，禮券亦鼓勵消費者(包括藍絲父母)在黃金圈消費<br />\n藍絲收到黃券唔用，多謝曬啦<br />\n甚至佢二手轉讓，按禮券成交價打折既慣例計，<br />\n最終都係願意兌換的手足得益<br />\n<br />\n心目中最佳平台係光時，佢地有實購購物券架！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkongs.com/collections/%E7%A6%AE%E5%93%81%E5%8D%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkongs.com%2Fcollections%2F%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E5%2593%2581%25E5%258D%25A1&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7Ead0DqFW0GAicD%2BCHpJjC4%3D&h=75a99a3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkongs.com/collections/%E7%A6%AE%E5%93%81%E5%8D%A1</a>"},{"pid":"2fdd5a2994c40361039b9c1b6c5b34999f33476b","tid":1809438,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T06:04:56.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"2418562fb25a9cccc29b098fbddcdcfb4eb9b8fe","tid":1809438,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fdd5a2994c40361039b9c1b6c5b34999f33476b","tid":1809438,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T06:04:56.000Z","msg":"正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T06:12:22.000Z","msg":"正就幫手推、甚至同你識既人周圍建議啦"},{"pid":"3228ce343e16901363bc5bc732bdb46202177272","tid":1809438,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2418562fb25a9cccc29b098fbddcdcfb4eb9b8fe","tid":1809438,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fdd5a2994c40361039b9c1b6c5b34999f33476b","tid":1809438,"uid":303982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim